info.description:
====================
silvatheme.silvadocs
====================

Silva Docs is a visual design (theme) for `Silva`_ 3 and higher. It is
used by default on the `Silva User Documentation`_.


Code repository
===============

The code for this extension can be found in Git:
https://github.com/silvacms/silvatheme.silvadocs


.. _Silva: http://silvacms.org
.. _Silva User Documentation: http://silvacms.org/docs/user/

Changelog
=========

1.0.2 (2013-08-26)
------------------

* Various updates, login form, images.

* Minify resources.

1.0.1 (2013-04-18)
------------------

* Cleanup form selectors.

* Add and style exit link.

1.0 (2012-12-11)
----------------

* Initial release
